We are Celestial Dynamics, a small and enthusiastic team of dreamers, visionaries and profound seekers with the mission to create beautiful and inspiring apps to raise awareness of earth, sky and the cosmos.
We respect the privacy of every person who visits this website and use our apps. All contact details will remain confidential. Any information you provide to us will not be sold or passed along to third parties.
