COSMIC WATCH APP
The Cosmic Watch App uses different App Permissions to operate. None of them will compromise your privacy. This information is not shared with us in any way.
App Permissions
Location >
to find out your location
• precise location (GPS and network-based)
We don’t store nor share any location information.
Storage  >
to save screenshots and don’t create screenshots with an existing name
• read the contents of your USB storage
• modify or delete the contents of your USB storage
• manage document storage
Other >
to check that your copy of the Cosmic Watch is legal and to share screenshots
• view network connections
• full network access
• Google Play license check
Personal Information
The Cosmic Watch App does not collect any personal information.
The App has a feature to share screenshots. This third party services may collect data about the user. You should always review the policies of third party products and services to make sure you are comfortable with the ways in which they collect and use your information.
Access to third party services' accounts allow this Application to access Data from your account on a third party service and perform actions with it. These services are not activated automatically, but require explicit authorization by the User.
